奖杯，那些失利也让我成长，让我学到了很多。我经历过很多困难的时刻，但巴萨生涯走向终点，我无法回来训练，无法再次踏上球场是最最艰难的一刻。新生活要开始了，但这一刻是最难的。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1fSX84n7qfU7EAMaCDY4NTU0MTYwIMPgvogGMBg4zQlAB3IJNDc4MjI5MjU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"375 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a7f427444b8c60c989f1b0ef9524ba3_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1628475543.407234","card_id":"Q_478040307","target":{"id":478040307,"title":"如何看待2020年东京奥运会女子艺术体操全能决赛俄罗斯选手迪娜负于以色列选手阿什兰姆获得银牌？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/478040307","type":"question","created":1628329659,"answer_count":49,"follower_count":217,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5548,25712,105508,160071,234364],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在2020年东京奥运会女子艺术体操全能决赛俄罗斯选手迪娜·阿维丽娜总分107.650以0.15分的差距负于以色列选手利诺伊·阿什兰姆的107.800收获银牌 同时以色列打破了俄罗斯对该项目长达20年的垄断。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1fSX84n7qfU7EAMaCDY4NTEyMDMwILutuYgGMAQ42QFACHIJNDc4MDQwMzA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"310 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-57b88ee27be4eb21cef4e7ee722cfc14_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1628475543.4078057","card_id":"Q_32209352","target":{"id":32209352,"title":"周大福、周生生、周大生、周六福、六福、金六福、金大福这些牌子有哪些区别？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/32209352","type":"question","created":1436883820,"answer_count":401,"follower_count":9237,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[10903,42855,99154,117267,199142],"comment_count":78,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0I1fSX84n7qfU7EAMaBzUwODMxOTcg7LaUrQUwTjiVSEAJcggzMjIwOTM1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"298 万热度","trend":0,"debut